suncertify.db.dao.comparator
Interface IComparator

All Known Implementing Classes:
IntegerComparator, MoneyComparator, TextComparator
public interface IComparator

IComparator provides method that allows to compare database fields without worrying about conversion from string to specific database field type. In order to obtain concrete comparator you should use appropriate factory instead of creating it using new operator.

Author:
Przemyslaw Bielicki
See Also:
